metadata.name: SUPERMAN
metadata.description:
SUPERMAN (feat. Paperhand Papi)

This song was conceived in the Freestyle Friday Space with the Outsider Collective and became a collaboration between Ayotemi and Outsider Collective founder Paperhand Papi.

The song is about breaking free of societal constraints and tapping in to your intrinsic power as a human being. SUPERMAN GOT NOTHING ON YOU!
